<p>
<a href="i-bex-0.1.13.tar.gz"><b>Download I-Bex Version 0.1.13</b></a>
</p>

<p>
I-Bex is a clone of the old DOS Game StoneAge for <a
href="http://sdlperl.org/">Perl/SDL</a>. It requires
<a href="http://www.libsdl.org/">SDL</a>, <a
href="http://www.perl.com/">Perl</a>, and Perl/SDL installed.
</p>

<p>
To run it type <tt>perl i-bex [board name]</tt> on the command line at
the code sub-directory. Currently, there are three boards available:
<tt>board.txt</tt>, <tt>board2.txt</tt> and <tt>board3.txt</tt>.
If you prepare more, please send them to me.
</p>

<p>
I-Bex is distributed under the MIT/X11 license.
</p>

